MY CONCENTRATION.

540
00:19:05,635 --> 00:19:07,668
SIT, BOY.

541
00:19:07,668 --> 00:19:10,068
SOTA, COME HERE A SEC.

542
00:19:10,068 --> 00:19:11,402
>> WHAT IS IT, KAGOME?

543
00:19:11,402 --> 00:19:13,368
>> KEEP INUYASHA COMPANY.

544
00:19:13,368 --> 00:19:14,402
>> SURE THING.

545
00:19:14,402 --> 00:19:15,435
I'LL SCRUB YOUR BACK

546
00:19:15,435 --> 00:19:16,568
IF YOU'LL SCRUB MINE.

547
00:19:16,568 --> 00:19:19,435
>> THANKS, SOTA.

548
00:19:19,435 --> 00:19:21,235
NOW, THEN.

549
00:19:21,235 --> 00:19:23,235
>> AAH! IT'S BOILING!

550
00:19:23,235 --> 00:19:27,068
WHAT'S HE TRYING TO DO TO ME?

551
00:19:27,068 --> 00:19:29,002
>> AAH!

552
00:19:29,002 --> 00:19:29,668
>> COME ON.

553
00:19:29,668 --> 00:19:31,168
YOU HAVE TO RINSE OFF THE SUDS.

554
00:19:31,168 --> 00:19:32,768
>> I'M NOT GOING BACK IN THERE!

555
00:19:32,768 --> 00:19:33,968
>> GET OUT!

556
00:19:33,968 --> 00:19:35,735
GET OUT OF HERE!

557
00:19:35,735 --> 00:19:36,435
UHH!

558
00:19:36,435 --> 00:19:39,335
>> HEY! UHH!

559
00:19:39,335 --> 00:19:41,602
>> OHH...

560
00:19:41,602 --> 00:19:42,835
OH, NOW I'VE FORGOTTEN

561
00:19:42,835 --> 00:19:44,068
EVERYTHING.

562
00:19:44,068 --> 00:19:47,635
OH!

563
00:19:47,635 --> 00:19:48,302
>> HUH?

564
00:19:48,302 --> 00:19:49,202
>> WOULD YOU LIKE SOMETHING

565
00:19:49,202 --> 00:19:50,902
TO EAT?

566
00:19:50,902 --> 00:19:51,835
>> IT'S SURE QUIET

567
00:19:51,835 --> 00:19:52,935
ALL OF A SUDDEN.

568
00:19:52,935 --> 00:19:55,702
>> AAH! WHAT WAS THAT?

569
00:19:55,702 --> 00:19:58,068
MY TONGUE'S ON FIRE!

570
00:19:58,068 --> 00:19:59,302
>> I GAVE HIM SOME CURRY,

571
00:19:59,302 --> 00:20:01,702
BUT MAYBE IT WAS TOO SPICY.

572
00:20:01,702 --> 00:20:02,368
>> THAT'S SURPRISING,

573
00:20:02,368 --> 00:20:03,635
COMING FROM A GUY WHO BLOWS OFF

574
00:20:03,635 --> 00:20:05,635
A GAPING HOLE IN HIS GUT.

575
00:20:05,635 --> 00:20:06,957
[SIGH]

576
00:20:24,211 --> 00:20:25,811
YOU KNOW...

577
00:20:25,811 --> 00:20:26,878
>> WHAT IS IT?

578
00:20:26,878 --> 00:20:28,478
I'M KEEPING QUIET.

579
00:20:28,478 --> 00:20:29,945
>> [THINKING] YEAH, BUT HOW AM I

580
00:20:29,945 --> 00:20:31,045
SUPPOSED TO CONCENTRATE WITH YOU

581
00:20:31,045 --> 00:20:32,578
STARING AT ME?

582
00:20:32,578 --> 00:20:33,645
WHY DON'T YOU LIE DOWN?

583
00:20:33,645 --> 00:20:34,945
>> NOT LIKELY.

584
00:20:34,945 --> 00:20:36,111
NOW, TURN AROUND AND GET BACK

585
00:20:36,111 --> 00:20:37,211
TO YOUR STUDIES.

586
00:20:37,211 --> 00:20:38,678
WE'RE GOING BACK TOMORROW.

587
00:20:38,678 --> 00:20:40,078
NO EXCUSES.

588
00:20:40,078 --> 00:20:45,645
>> HA HA! OK.

589
00:20:45,645 --> 00:20:46,911
[THINKING] IS HE ACTUALLY GONNA

590
00:20:46,911 --> 00:20:48,045
SIT THERE AND WATCH OVER ME

591
00:20:48,045 --> 00:20:49,278
ALL NIGHT?

592
00:20:49,278 --> 00:20:50,545
I WOULDN'T PUT IT PAST HIM.

593
00:20:50,545 --> 00:20:52,027
HE'S ALWAYS GOT ENERGY TO BURN.

594
00:21:01,511 --> 00:21:04,211
HUH? HE'S ASLEEP.

595
00:21:04,211 --> 00:21:06,811
>> [SNORING]

596
00:21:06,811 --> 00:21:08,045
>> [THINKING] HUH!

597
00:21:08,045 --> 00:21:09,511
WHAT'S WITH HIM?

598
00:21:09,511 --> 00:21:10,945
HE BUGS ME CONSTANTLY,

599
00:21:10,945 --> 00:21:12,278
AND HE CHOOSES NOW OF ALL TIMES

600
00:21:12,278 --> 00:21:13,520
TO FLAKE OUT ON ME.

601
00:21:21,411 --> 00:21:23,511
I'VE NEVER SEEN INUYASHA SLEEP

602
00:21:23,511 --> 00:21:24,712
SO SOUNDLY.

603
00:21:33,611 --> 00:21:35,111
I GUESS HE'S MORE TIRED

604
00:21:35,111 --> 00:21:40,578
THAN THE REST OF US.

605
00:21:40,578 --> 00:21:41,911
HAVE A GOOD SLEEP,

606
00:21:41,911 --> 00:21:43,452
IF ONLY FOR THE NIGHT.

607
00:21:56,611 --> 00:21:58,545
>> KAGOME AND INUYASHA ARE BACK.

608
00:21:58,545 --> 00:21:59,511
>> OH.

609
00:21:59,511 --> 00:22:00,711
SO, YOU SPENT THE NIGHT

610
00:22:00,711 --> 00:22:02,245
AT KAGOME'S HOUSE, DID YOU?

611
00:22:02,245 --> 00:22:03,511
>> WHAT'S WRONG, KAGOME?

612
00:22:03,511 --> 00:22:04,911
WHERE ARE THE SMILES?

613
00:22:04,911 --> 00:22:05,711
>> WHERE DO YOU THINK?

614
00:22:05,711 --> 00:22:07,045
YOU WERE HOGGING THE WHOLE BED,

615
00:22:07,045 --> 00:22:07,978
AND I DIDN'T GET A MINUTE'S

616
00:22:07,978 --> 00:22:08,978
SLEEP.

617
00:22:08,978 --> 00:22:09,911
ON TOP OF WHICH,

618
00:22:09,911 --> 00:22:11,411
THE TEST WAS A KILLER.

619
00:22:11,411 --> 00:22:15,578
MAN, MY LIFE STINKS!

620
00:22:15,578 --> 00:22:18,878
>> A-AT LEAST IT'S SUNNY.

621
00:22:26,860 --> 00:22:33,693
>> [SINGING IN JAPANESE]

622
00:22:33,693 --> 00:22:36,227
♪ EVERY HEART ♪

623
00:22:36,227 --> 00:22:47,127
[SINGING IN JAPANESE]

624
