♪ EVERY HEART ♪

625
00:22:49,693 --> 00:23:59,289
[SINGING IN JAPANESE]

626
00:23:59,289 --> 00:23:59,889
>> HERE'S A QUESTION.

627
00:23:59,889 --> 00:24:00,869
BESIDES THE JEWEL SHARDS

628
00:24:00,869 --> 00:24:02,335
NARAKU HAS IN HIS POSSESSION,

629
00:24:02,335 --> 00:24:03,602
WHO ELSE HAS SOME,

630
00:24:03,602 --> 00:24:05,069
AND HOW MANY DO THEY HAVE?

631
00:24:05,069 --> 00:24:07,035
>> WELL, KOHAKU HAS ONE.

632
00:24:07,035 --> 00:24:08,169
KAGOME HAS 3.

633
00:24:08,169 --> 00:24:09,335
LET'S SEE.

634
00:24:09,335 --> 00:24:10,069
>> TIME'S UP.

635
00:24:10,069 --> 00:24:11,402
YOU FORGOT ABOUT KOGA,

636
00:24:11,402 --> 00:24:12,935
WHO HAS ONE IN EACH LEG.

637
00:24:12,935 --> 00:24:13,969
>> THAT MEANS NARAKU

638
00:24:13,969 --> 00:24:15,535
WILL GO AFTER KOGA, TOO.

639
00:24:15,535 --> 00:24:17,035
>> YES, EXCEPT THAT NARAKU

640
00:24:17,035 --> 00:24:18,235
HAS DISAPPEARED.

641
00:24:18,235 --> 00:24:19,435
>> THEN WHAT'S THAT?

